          "type": "text",
          "text": "You are identifying a houseplant from a photo. Respond with ONLY a JSON object (no prose, no markdown fences) with this exact shape:\n{\n  \"species\": \"<scientific name or null>\",\n  \"common_name\": \"<common name or null>\",\n  \"confidence\": <0..1>,\n  \"care_notes\": \"<2-3 sentence care summary: light, water, humidity>\",\n  \"growth\": { \"height_cm\": <number or null>, \"leaf_count\": <integer or null> }\n}\nIf you can't tell, set fields to null and confidence to 0."
